Join us in our HR’s Benefits Service team to support the administration of staff benefits in DSTA, including leave, medical and flexible benefits. The role will require you to:

• Ensure smooth implementation of staff benefits administration according to the latest policies and guidelines
• Be part of team to support business centre account 
• Communicate effectively to different stakeholders relating to benefits and IT support areas 
• Ensure timely and accurate processing of benefits claims 
• Support the digitisation efforts in the areas of go-green initiative and automation of work processes initiative

Requirements
• Good IT knowledge and skills, preferably in SAP System
• Good interpersonal and communication skills
• Meticulous and thrives in a fast-paced and dynamic environment
• Qualification in Human Resource, Business Administration or Business related disciplines